info.author: Daneel S. Yaitskov
info.description:
pafo is a help debug library. it allows programmer to observer state's data
fields of a complex object or a bundle of objects. Even if some
objects in the bundle haven't __str__ or __repr__ methods. Such
situation is very usual. Nobody want to writer code only that to print
the state of an object two-three times.
info.name: pafo
info.summary: library recursively prints data fields of an objects
